<!--
    Option E — "N" monogram (Net Worth)
    Three bold strokes forming the letter N.
    Minimal, brandable, unique among finance apps.

    ╻       ╻
    ╻╲      ╻
    ╻  ╲    ╻
    ╻    ╲  ╻
    ╻      ╲╻
    ╹       ╹
